name: The Golden Gander, Hand-Painted Vintage Clutch Purse
description:
Every girl needs a go-to piece of arm candy, and this shimmering vintage clutch is just that. This upcycled vintage purse (with an optional chain strap) is the perfect accessory for any night out. Spruce up some skinny jeans or adorn a little-black-dress, this purse is hand-painted with quality leather paints. Big enough for a smart phone, wallet, compact, lipstick, and a few other unmentionables.

*As always, a DEAPT original design.
*This is a one-of-a-kind item.
*This is an up cycled product (minor wear is normal, but we go to great lengths to ensure our final products are impeccable and will leave you satisfied).

name: Spring Fever Feathers, Leather Earrings
description:
Gorgeous in green leather, with cream to pink ombre feather design.
These new, painted, leather-feather earrings measure over 3 inches,  and come in a super-flattering silhouette. Perfectly paired with a messy up-do, simple blouse, and skinny jeans.


One-of-a-kind earrings, individually hand-painted, and hand-cut from quality leathers.
As always, an original DEAPT design


(Photo of model is for size reference, not color. Photo by Annika Erikson)

name: Give Me Shellter, Limited Edition, Vintage Gold-Painted Sea Shells
description:
So... we're shopping in a little vintage store alongside a highway. We begin conversation with the little grey haired lady behind the counter.  After a short discussion, she pulls out a shallow, wooden cigar-box full of sea shells. Vintage sea shells. Vintage sea shells hand painted in 24kt gold. 
We've put these shells on sparkling vintage chains for you.
Truly extraordinary.

name: Jurassic Pink Necklace
description:
You've never seen anything like this before. In DoeEyed's signature style, this necklace is all kindsa badass disguised by some slick pink paint and delicately placed rhinestones.

This saber tooth pendant is cast in resin, dipped in paint, wire-wrapped, and topped with rhinestones. And the icing in the cake? The dual-sided clasp-closure and extra long, luxurious curb chain make this a necklace that can be worn short (on model), or oh-so long.

As always, a DEAPT original design.

name: Blue Kyanite Shard Pendants on Vintage Chains
description:
!!Limited Edition!!

Stunning, natural Blue Kyanite shards, delicately hand-wrapped in gold wire are hung from vintage chains. Bohemian glamour at its finest. 
Stones are approx 2 inches each.

A DEAPT webshop exclusive design.
